cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: The paper discusses the creation of a dataset for inter-personal relationship extraction, which involves natural language processing and information extraction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also mentions knowledge graph construction, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of machine learning and annotation also suggests the sub-categories cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as possible categories.
